Question
1:
Student Marks Processing (Vectors)
Scenario
A lecturer stores marks of students in a single subject and wants to calculate:
Total marks
Average marks
Highest marks
Question
Which data structure is suitable and how is it implemented in R?
Answer
Vector is suitable because all values are of the same data type.
marks <- c(78, 85, 90, 88, 76)
total <- sum(marks)
average <- mean(marks)
highest <- max(marks)
total
average
highest
 
