Question
3:
Employee Profile Storage (Lists)
Scenario
An HR system needs to store mixed data types for an employee:
Employee ID
Name
Salary
Department
Question
Which data structure should be used?
Answer
List is suitable because it supports different data types.
employee <- list(
ID = 101,
Name = "Gayathri",
Salary = 45000,
Department = "IT"
)
employee
employee$Name
employee$Salary
 
